"title": "8298: love, for one another",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8298: love, for one another",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Scripture instructs God's people to love one another and illustrates what this means in practice.</p>\n<h2>Reasons for loving one another</h2>\n<h3>God commands it</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:14\">GAL 5:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:18\">LEV 19:18</a>LEV <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:34\">19:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut10:19\">DEU 10:19</a>\n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:39\">MAT 22:39</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:31\">MRK 12:31</a> <em>the second greatest commandment</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:12\">JHN 15:12</a> <em>Jesus Christ commands his disciples to love one another</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom13:10\">ROM 13:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:9\">1TH 4:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:1\">HEB 13:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas2:8\">JAS 2:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:22\">1PE 1:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:17\">1PE 2:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:23\">1JN 3:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:21\">1JN 4:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2John1:5\">2JN 1:5</a></p>\n<h3>God has taken the initiative in showing love</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:11\">1JN 4:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal2:10\">MAL 2:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor8:11-1Cor8:13\">1CO 8:11–8:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:16\">1JN 3:16</a></p>\n<h3>God's people are known by their love</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:35\">JHN 13:35</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:10\">1JN 2:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:14\">1JN 3:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:7\">1JN 4:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:16\">1JN 4:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:20\">1JN 4:20</a></p>\n<h3>Love maintains fellowship</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:8\">1PE 4:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:12\">PRO 10:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov17:9\">PRO 17:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:2\">EPH 4:2</a></p>\n<h3>Love promotes sacrificial service</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:8\">1TH 2:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov17:17\">PRO 17:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor12:15\">2CO 12:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:13\">GAL 5:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:30\">PHP 2:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:10\">PHP 4:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess1:3\">1TH 1:3</a></p>\n<h2>Expressing love for one another</h2>\n<h3>In caring for the sick</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:36\">MAT 25:36</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job2:11\">JOB 2:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:14\">GAL 4:14</a></p>\n<h3>In meeting material needs</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:35\">MAT 25:35</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut15:7-Deut15:8\">DEU 15:7–15:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:17\">1JN 3:17</a></p>\n<h3>In affectionate greetings</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor13:12\">2CO 13:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen33:4\">GEN 33:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen45:14-Gen45:15\">GEN 45:14–45:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:37\">ACT 20:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom16:16\">ROM 16:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor16:20\">1CO 16:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:14\">1PE 5:14</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of the demonstration of love for one another</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen14:14-Gen14:16\">GEN 14:14–14:16</a> <em>Abraham for Lot</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod32:31-Exod32:32\">EXO 32:31–32:32</a> <em>Moses for Israel</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam18:3\">1SA 18:3</a> <em>Jonathan</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:2-Luke7:6\">LUK 7:2–7:6</a> <em>the Roman centurion for his servant</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:29-Luke10:37\">LUK 10:29–10:37</a> <em>the good Samaritan</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:32\">ACT 4:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:33\">ACT 16:33</a> <em>the Philippian jailer</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:38\">ACT 20:38</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom16:4\">ROM 16:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor2:4\">2CO 2:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:15\">EPH 1:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:8\">PHP 1:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:1\">PHP 4:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:16-2Tim1:17\">2TI 1:16–1:17</a> <em>Onesiphorus</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phlm1:12\">PHM 1:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/3John1:6\">3JN 1:6</a></p>\n<h3>Paul's love for his churches</h3>\n<p>Corinth:\n <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:3-2Cor1:6\">2CO 1:3–1:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor2:4\">2CO 2:4</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:19\">GAL 4:19</a> <em>Galatia</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:3\">PHP 1:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:7\">PHP 1:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:1\">PHP 4:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:7-1Thess2:8\">1TH 2:7–2:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess3:7-1Thess3:10\">1TH 3:7–3:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess3:12\">1TH 3:12</a></p>",
